snippet.title: Sausage Wars | Official Gameplay Trailer | Nintendo Switch™
snippet.description:
An Epic Sausage Battle till the last drop of ketchup for up to 4 Players and 20 Bots! Careful - it’s a hot-dog-eat-hot-dog world out there. So fight to the death and push them all till your enemies are oozing Tomato Blood!!
https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/sausage-wars-switch/
